{"lastModified":1748861613060,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nThe Lagoon 46 opens up endless cruising possibilities, designed to accompany you, your family, and friends on unforgettable journeys across the world’s most beautiful seas, offering unmatched comfort and performance for every adventure.\n\nA Dream Realized\n\nSatisfy your longing for open waters, your curiosity to discover uncharted destinations, and your desire to explore the hidden shores of the world’s most breathtaking islands. Step aboard a catamaran where excellence in reliability and comfort sets the standard. Your journey starts here.\n\nInnovation: the new furling boom improves your sailing experience\n\nDestined for the Lagoon 46 and Lagoon 51, the mechanism of this boom is not hidden by a cover, but remains visible, a unique concept for greater ease of use.\n\nThis particularity offers multiple advantages, notably the ability to observe and control reefing, furling, and other sail handling operations with great precision.\n\nExpansive horizons\n\nPerfectly integrated into the deck line, the cockpit affords an exceptional view of the horizon. The flybridge of the Lagoon 46 offers two functionalities in one space, with transformable sundecks and a full helm station: the perfect balance of comfort and ergonomic design for easy handling.\n\nLife on the terrace\n\nWith a generous storage capacity, sliding bench seating, and an exterior galley… the cockpit of the Lagoon 46 is a truly inviting modular living space, able to accommodate up to twelve people. In this shared living area, each person will find the perfect spot for creating treasured summer memories.\n\nFull comfort\n\nThe Lagoon 46 conceals an unparalleled interior volume for a catamaran in this category. Comfortable furnishings and fine materials welcome guests in a refined atmosphere, while maintaining the practicality and functionality of each living space on board.","blueprint":{"name":"ESCAPE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0ee8920-3a76-11f0-8537-73a7fad38f8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0ecdb70-3a76-11f0-8536-73a7fad38f8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0ed9ec0-3a76-11f0-8536-73a7fad38f8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0edece0-3a76-11f0-8536-73a7fad38f8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0ecb460-3a76-11f0-8536-73a7fad38f8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b135f260-3a76-11f0-8a6e-5591cc8c4b87/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b134b9e0-3a76-11f0-b8c1-074e634c694c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0f036d0-3a76-11f0-8537-73a7fad38f8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0eed740-3a76-11f0-8537-73a7fad38f8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b12a59a0-3a76-11f0-aa2d-5161380997eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0f05de0-3a76-11f0-8537-73a7fad38f8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b12d18c0-3a76-11f0-aa2d-5161380997eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0f60330-3a76-11f0-b8c1-074e634c694c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::b0ee6210-3a76-11f0-8536-73a7fad38f8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b7994290-3a73-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::